snippet.title: I Cannot Drown Trailer
snippet.description:
Download at Itch.io: https://pureiceblue.itch.io/i-cannot-drown
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/pureiceblue
Development Blog: https://allegrezza-harmony.tumblr.com/

Your name is Ume. You are in a world. It is a familiar yet unknown world. Stretch your legs and go for a walk.

I Cannot Drown was created for Dream Diary Jam 3. It was really fun to work on something completely unrelated to Allegrezza Harmony and something that allows me to go buck wild horror wise. I hope you all enjoy the project :).

Trailer Music by https://www.sougetsu-on.net/
